Class Track

java.lang.Object
app.tracktune.model.track.Track
public class Track extends Object
Represents a musical track entity with basic metadata.

Each Track has a unique identifier (nullable for new tracks before insertion), a title, creation timestamp, and an associated user ID who owns the track.
